  "title": "STEERSMAN / ENGINE DRIVER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for the operation of the vessel and safety guidelines.</li>\n  <li>Maintain and upkeep the condition of the vessel.</li>\n  <li>Comply with all MPA and statutory regulations at all time.</li>\n  <li>Comply with company's (safety) guidelines and procedures.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a valid MPA Helmsman/Steersman/Engine Driver (Port Limit) Certificate.</li>\n  <li>Well organised and punctual.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of experience operating crew boat.</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and public holidays.</li>\n  <li>Added advantage if have basic survival skills.</li>\n  <li>Singaporeans only.</li>\n</ul>",
